<p align="center"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">English Translation</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;">The  angered Lord came as a wild boar and lifted the freshly decked Dame  Earth who was held captive in the ocean. Those who wish to attain his  lotus feet, Hearken! Go to Tillai Tiruchitrakudam surrounded by  gold-and-gem mansions, where the crowned Pallava king offers worship  with gold, gems and pearls.</span></p></div><span class="article_separator">&nbsp;</span>
